            "title": "白宮未對俄羅斯液化天然氣進一步動手 中國繼續推進進口",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"白宮未對俄羅斯液化天然氣進一步動手 中國繼續推進進口\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E9bwuVXO8Y_IW0KARkxN5A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/c77eece0-b003-11f0-9cfc-e17385f27f80\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">白宮未對俄羅斯液化天然氣進一步動手 中國繼續推進進口</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
