        {
            "title": "泡泡瑪特創半年最大單日跌幅　傳內地盲盒熱度降溫｜港股異動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"泡泡瑪特人氣IP「LABUBU」在全球爆紅。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AQeDaR0Y0NxOMdk3VCMDng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/am730_578/4ca0791c7d238abd005706ebb8f89972\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">泡泡瑪特人氣IP「LABUBU」在全球爆紅。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>人氣玩偶LABUBU的母公司<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:泡泡瑪特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/泡泡瑪特\">泡泡瑪特</a>(</span></span></span></span></span>POP MART<span><span><span><span><span>, 9992)日前公布未經審核第三季整體收益，按年增245%至250%，惟市場憂慮其增長放緩，加上內地網傳盲盒熱度降溫，導致泡泡瑪特的股價今日(23日)再受壓，一度低見228.6元，跌10.8%，創約6個月最大單日跌幅，半日報232.2元，仍挫逾9%，在一眾</span></span></span></span></span>藍籌中表現最弱。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">市場憂增長放緩</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>泡泡瑪特於周二(21日)收報250.4元，跌8%。收市後公司發布上季營運數據，指季內收入按年增加介乎2.45倍至2.5倍。數據公布後，多間大行發表報告唱好，其中花旗更將目標價升至415元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dc9aeae4-047b-38ef-b014-f1ffb922333f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>然而，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>《彭博》引述晨星分析師Jeff Zhang認為，上季泡泡瑪特收入增幅勝市場預期，但投資者或憂慮未來數季增長放緩。他補充，預料泡泡瑪特收入增幅於今年見頂，明年起增長放緩。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>資料來源：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:泡泡瑪特公告;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2025/1021/2025102100237_c.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">泡泡瑪特公告</a></span></span></span></span></span></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/泡泡瑪特創半年最大單日跌幅-傳內地盲盒熱度降溫-港股異動/611287?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/泡泡瑪特創半年最大單日跌幅-傳內地盲盒熱度降溫-港股異動/611287?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/泡泡瑪特創半年最大單日跌幅-傳內地盲盒熱度降溫-港股異動/611287?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%91%AA%E7%89%B9%E5%89%B5%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85-%E5%82%B3%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%B2%E7%9B%92%E7%86%B1%E5%BA%A6%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E7%95%B0%E5%8B%95-040200948.html",
